#20652
Pathway of Chaos~
From this vintage point, the city seems to span on into oblivion, never
ending in the darkness of black magic and the occasional burst of faerie
fire.  Several shadows lurk beside you, each with dancing crimson eyes that
follow you wherever you pass.  This is Sinaerth-Kasah, the city of the drow
within the Realm of Clandestine, and like so many other cities engulfed in
darkness, the inhabitants here are encased in their own shells of
self-preservation and subservience to Lolth.  Many sections of the city are
blocked off by mounted drow guards upon large lizards, allowing passage into
only the central section of the city.  Two streets branch off to the north
and south, weaving through the endless shadows of the city.
~
