#20653
SiNelirae Street~
 This street is somewhat plain in comparison to the other streets in the
central city.  The southern section of the city's center seems devoted to
the warriors, a force that uses brute strength rather than the magical drow
intrigue looked highly upon by the nobles.  Despite this, the glow of faerie
fire still spills out into the streets, bathing this section of the city in
a cold, magical glow.  The street continues to the west, and another street
branches off to the north, toward the entrance of the city.
~
