#20654
SiNelirae Street~
This subtly ornate street running through the city's southern side is
filled with many drow, each one bearing the emblem of the academy of
warfare.  The stone buildings here are less refined, almost crude compared
to the rest of the city, but the outline of faerie fire still filters down
into the streets.  A modest house lies to the south, filled with the banter
of a typical drow household, and the street continues to the east and west. 
A link has been carved through an enchanted stone border to the north,
allowing passage into the marketplace of the city.
~
