#20657
SiNelirae Street~
The street suddenly turns almost crude in comparison to the rest of the
central city's streets.  The houses and buildings that rise here are still
lined in the typical outline of faerie fire, but the stone has mostly been
left unchiseled and unformed, giving a raw appearance.  A particularly large
building rises to the north, where many drow soldiers filter in and out. 
The sound of metal against metal reverberates through the air, a sign that
swordplay is common here.  The street continues to the east, and another
street branches off to the west.
~
