#20720
Entrance to Sinaerth~
The fabled Drow City opens up before you to the west, basking in an
unholy glory bestowed upon the demonic race by their wicked deity Lolth.
The city itself is carved almost entirely out of ore and stone, gleaming in
the magical light of the faerie fire that lines the large homes of each
individual family.  A large gate blocks entry to the west, protecting yet
almost daring any unlucky traveler to enter its domain.  The drow are the
masters of stealth and the shadows that lurk around you are most likely
Lolth's most trusted of servants, waiting to pounce upon those that tread
upon their home.  An exit into a bright land lies to the east, offering
sanctuary where there is none.
~
